    cardOutNE: Pgrm Guide III
    cardOutNC: "\u300A\u5165\u95E8\u5230\u5165\u571F\u300B\u4E09"
    cardNameEng: Game Engine Architecture
    cardNameChi: "\u300A\u6E38\u620F\u5F15\u64CE\u67B6\u6784\u300B"
    cardSummaryEng: "In this new and improved third edition of the highly popular\_Game
      Engine Architecture, Jason Gregory draws on his nearly two decades of experience
      at Midway, Electronic Arts and Naughty Dog to present both the theory and practice
      of game engine software development. In this book, the broad range of technologies
      and techniques used by AAA game studios are each explained in detail, and their
      roles within a real industrial-strength game engine are illustrated."
    cardSummaryChi: "\u6B64\u4E3A\u975E\u5E38\u53D7\u6B22\u8FCE\u7684\u6E38\u620F\u5F15\u64CE\u67B6\u6784\u56FE\u4E66\u7684\u7B2C\u4E09\u7248\uFF0C\u4F5C\u8005Jason
